# Local, private test data (gitignored)

This directory holds **real** game save files copied from your own installations,
kept locally for manual and integration testing. Its contents are gitignored — only
this `.gitkeep` is committed, to preserve the folder.

Do **not** commit real game save data here. Committed automated tests should use
**synthetic** fixtures (built in code from the documented format) so the test suite
never depends on a specific user's files or ships game data.

Example (kept locally, ignored): `PLAYER1.U1`
